{"tid":2137260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文慎入] 如果最終係拜登當選，可能會對香港更加有利","createTime":"2020-08-02T20:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T08:05:00.000Z","uid":52658,"like":7,"dislike":101,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"fead5cb27ddf836cfeb530553192a5cb49af0a8a","tid":2137260,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:17:03.000Z","msg":"利申先 我係川粉黎<br />\n廢事比人話我五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜你地真係覺得川普好撚反共咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記唔記得當初係邊個話唔想插手香港事務<br />\n邊個話台灣係筆尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋你地又記唔記得當初G20 <br />\n川普隻字不提香港<br />\n反而係安倍同歐盟有主動問維尼熊關於香港既事<br />\n<br />\n無錯佢呢幾個月係做左好多野<br />\n但我覺得只係做show多<br />\n因為佢真係唔夠雷厲風行<br />\n<br />\n川普既行事方式 諗下佢當初起圍牆 退tpp同搞鳩歐盟<br />\n所以以川普既性格<br />\n佢真係有心做既 佢係絕對唔會同你拖泥帶水 慢慢同你磨<br />\n呢條友講野一時一樣<br />\n所以佢選完之後會唔會變另一個樣 真係無人知<br />\n真正反共既 係蓬佩奧同共和黨班國會議員<br />\n而唔係川普本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反拜登<br />\n無錯佢係唔夠川普咁強硬<br />\n但佢有一樣好<br />\n就係一旦拜登當選 佢好大機會會同盟友修補關係<br />\n呢樣野比起美國孤身作戰 更加有效去圍堵中國<br />\n因為川普在任四年<br />\n美國兩黨既關係 甚至係同國際上盟友既關係<br />\n係前所未有既低點<br />\n<br />\n而家抗中係兩黨共識<br />\n得罪講句 拜登都8張幾野 又有老人痴呆<br />\n佢只會係民主黨手上既傀儡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估d美國人真係好撐佢咩？<br />\n投比佢既只係反川普既賭爛票咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我當佢真係想舔共 我唔覺得佢會有能力敵得過成個民主黨內部既壓力<br />\n<br />\n而川普佢既個人色彩太濃烈 <br />\n佢係共和黨裡面根本就不受控<br />\n如果拜登真係會舔共既<br />\n你覺得英國 澳洲同加拿大會突然間變得咁強硬咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁 <br />\n不過身為一個川粉 我都會希望會係由川普當選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為拜登既未知性比川普高<br />\n雖然我無票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但見到你班友係咁話民主黨舔共 拜登比中共收買左<br />\n真係忍唔住出篇長文黎屌醒呢班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過美國既政治 我唔算好熟<br />\n呢度一定有人會比我更加清楚<br />\n希望有人會認真一齊分析下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打左好耐架"},{"pid":"283f0f935d5e3987b43b6db563ca29210c66a462","tid":2137260,"uid":143343,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:18:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26e355219ef5dfe853ac1a0c7ce392920db7bd74","tid":2137260,"uid":143343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:19:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0eb90444a6eedb8fbc95823057c50452fa6c81a6","tid":2137260,"uid":191815,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:19:54.000Z","msg":"拜登老人痴呆㗎啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7a9664acb1703354eda3b47618df52b1673863","tid":2137260,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"283f0f935d5e3987b43b6db563ca29210c66a462","tid":2137260,"uid":143343,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:18:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:20:30.000Z","msg":"你咪慢慢起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你睇左我講乜先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你覺得我講錯既歡迎屌鳩返我轉頭"},{"pid":"d0259bc75a715c2f33d69ab65f209fb6b6b43085","tid":2137260,"uid":235391,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:20:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">川普<br />\nwho?</span></span>"},{"pid":"2cbf53a3411a2c795f05303a9b9413bb363f9251","tid":2137260,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"0eb90444a6eedb8fbc95823057c50452fa6c81a6","tid":2137260,"uid":191815,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:19:54.000Z","msg":"拜登老人痴呆㗎啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:24:10.000Z","msg":"佢有無老人痴呆從來都唔係一個問題<br />\n我上面講左"},{"pid":"16cdf92c2d051a624c733013f684520603332ed3","tid":2137260,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"26e355219ef5dfe853ac1a0c7ce392920db7bd74","tid":2137260,"uid":143343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:19:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:26:43.000Z","msg":"你都戇鳩 <br />\n我屌鳩國民黨d post又唔見你拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙重間諜咩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c013e374a282b0a6798d62fe9b924177a1b14708","tid":2137260,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:28:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d866d201e6c53c52377ec409082e1b2762320c7c","tid":2137260,"uid":116466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:29:23.000Z","msg":"拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0508fdf2debe8c72073e7b579237a45e5e0adb93","tid":2137260,"uid":270889,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:33:57.000Z","msg":"笑咗<br />\n打句&quot;利申先 我係川粉&quot;就想洗底"},{"pid":"bc352fee081f32b31a10c3a80a514c5555383827","tid":2137260,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:35:31.000Z","msg":"白痴仔，拉"},{"pid":"3eb86ae9412765e64f728423627139e43999dd0b","tid":2137260,"uid":175621,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T20:35:58.000Z","msg":"先唔理你係咪5毛<br />\n即管回下你<br />\n<br />\n你話抗共係2 黨共識，首先其實冇人實質調查過究竟係唔係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/